-- enumFromTo_ :: Enum a => a -> a -> [a]
on enumFromTo_(m, n)
    if m â‰¤ n then
        set x to fromEnum(m)
        set y to fromEnum(n)
        set xs to {}
        repeat with i from x to y
            set end of xs to i
        end repeat
        map(toEnum(m), xs)
    else
        return {}
    end if
end enumFromTo
